FBIS4-8706 "dreeu074_y_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Federal Declaration on Air Strikes Adopted Declaration on Air Strikes Adopted LD1504123294 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in Serbo-Croatian 1133 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504123294 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpts] Belgrade, 15 Apr (TANJUG) -- The Chamber of Republics of the Federal Assembly today adopted a declaration vehemently condemning the NATO air strikes against the Serbs in former Bosnia-Herzegovina carried out under UN auspices that caused destruction and casualties among the civilian population. [passage omitted] The declaration was supported by 28 deputies; two voted against. The same document was adopted by the Chamber of Citizens of the Federal Assembly yesterday.
